title: A special Joe Rogan Experience Review of Bill Burr
description:
This is a special episode of JRE Review as we talk about Bill Burr's new comedy special and it's impact on comedy. It's amazing so make sure to watch it NOW on Netflix.

Enjoy my review folks!
